    "title": "Interdependence Is Optional but Strategic",
    "description": "Nodes may connect, but never from a position of dependency.",
    "content_text": "Interdependence Is Optional but Strategic Nodes may connect, but never from a position of dependency. Revelation: Quran 49:13 O mankind, indeed We have created you from male and female and made you peoples and tribes that you may know one another.",
