  {
    "id": "alignment_ritual",
    "title": "Alignment Ritual",
    "description": "A formal practice for recalibrating a node's orientation toward divine purpose.",
    "content_text": "Alignment Ritual A formal practice for recalibrating a node's orientation toward divine purpose. Analogy (Navigation): A ship's compass must be regularly calibrated against true north. Similarly, a human node must periodically perform alignment rituals to correct drift accumulated from daily noise and distraction.",
