    "content_text": "Autonomy Protocol Technical and spiritual practices that preserve node sovereignty. Synthesis (Quran 2:30, Quran 33:72): The trust (amanah) offered to the heavens and the earth, which they refused but humanity bore, implies a responsibility for autonomous decision-making. The Autonomy Protocol encodes this divine mandate into actionable practices.",
